g 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cyberpunk-2077-updat-e2.0-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cd-projekt-red">CD Projekt Red</a>正在考虑在即将推出的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cyberpunk-2077">《赛博朋克 2077》</a></em>续作中添加多人游戏的可能性。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/persona-3-reload-preview-interview-3571048">《女神异闻录 3：重装版》将成为必玩重制版</a></strong></li></ul><p>CD Projekt Red 首席执行官 Adam Badowski 在接受<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/cd-projekt-aims-start-production-phase-polaris-2024-2024-01-22/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>采访时表示，计划在今年年底前让 80 名员工参与续作的制作，公司“考虑加入多人游戏元素”。不过，巴多夫斯基没有进一步详细说明。</p><p>有趣的是，最初的<em>《赛博朋克 2077》</em>计划推出多人游戏。在发布之前，该游戏被确认将获得专用的多人游戏模式。在发布时，该模式被升级为完全独立的体验，然后最终完全从计划中完全删除。</p><p>近日， <em>《赛博朋克 2077》</em>叙事总监伊戈尔·萨辛斯基 (Igor Sarzyński) 简单谈到了游戏的续作， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-sequel-has-officially-started-development-3510476">代号为“Project Orion”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3514686" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514686" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3514686" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-1392x